Any questions? >>>

FAQs

  • What can I do on Accrue?

    With Accrue, you can send and receive money across Africa, in minutes. You can create virtual USD cards and fund it with MoMo, MPESA, bank transfer, or stablecoins. You can save in dollars and earn up to 7% annual interest.

  • How long does it take for me to do a cross-border payment?

    Most payouts on Accrue complete in less than five minutes.

  • How many countries are available?

    Accrue is available in 9 African countries (Nigeria, Ghana, South Africa, Kenya, Cameroon, Rwanda, Tanzania, Uganda, Zambia). We are expanding to more African countries soon and we will keep you updated.

  • Where can I use my Accrue Card?

    You can use your Accrue Card for payments anywhere that Mastercard/Visa debit cards are accepted. This includes popular platforms such as Amazon, Google, YouTube, AliExpress, Alibaba, Zara, Fashion Nova, Shein, Udemy, Gothenburg University, and many more!

  • How safe are my funds?

    Your funds, transactions, and private information are protected by state-of-the-art security technology that powers some of the biggest services in the world.

  • Can I withdraw my money instantly?

    Yes! You can withdraw your money to your bank, mobile money, or M-Pesa account within minutes.
